{"tid":1466923,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"核彈都唔割","createTime":"2019-08-13T16:59:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T17:05:01.000Z","uid":93540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"e4d18ff879add8880949e904119e684b69893d2e","tid":1466923,"uid":93540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:59:59.000Z","msg":"講咁耐到底幾時先做到<br />\n睇下對家點樣演繹核彈都唔割<br />\n黑警記招兜大圈護自己夥計<br />\n藍絲文宣抺黑勇武 顛倒是非黑白<br />\n零指責黑警做過既野<br />\n<br />\n我想講我都唔讚成機場私刑打人<br />\n但你問我立場有冇因為咁而變？<br />\n我都係冇撚變過 都係核彈都唔撚會割！<br />\n我明白現場係有好多鬼煽動大家<br />\n但希望大家冷靜唔好比憤怒令自己變成最憎既果種人<br />\n<br />\n呢場運動相信大家既立場已經歸左邊<br />\n只要大家唔割席 堅持立場<br />\n做錯既 再反思 改善 做得更好<br />\n呢場運動我地一定要贏！"},{"pid":"04653e8e612b1eb1fd843e9276e42d7a30d6601c","tid":1466923,"uid":93540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:00:47.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">核彈都唔割</span>"},{"pid":"cbf385def52712644a2387374c7d7d33a2b70a17","tid":1466923,"uid":93540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:00:58.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">核彈都唔割</span>"},{"pid":"b8543df1557fb266406603085bd6ce47dc8e9341","tid":1466923,"uid":93540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:01:11.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">核彈都唔割</span>"},{"pid":"2210a9cf0dd18a96c6b3fcd4cfd7a486a7422a35","tid":1466923,"uid":93540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:02:28.000Z","msg":"希望大家真係講得出 做得得<br />\n唔好因為前線一次錯誤就打算割<br />\n無論點都應該支持 有錯我地事後再反思！"},{"pid":"891860e30489e53d44f6ce9b16364dac211cb246","tid":1466923,"uid":93540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:02:59.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">核彈都唔割</span>"},{"pid":"d2de15a0954e45858ada5fc5a1db3f5b260f988d","tid":1466923,"uid":93540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:03:12.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">核彈都唔割</span>"},{"pid":"a9